---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="反馈" description="联系 GM Shrek 获取反馈、支持或建议。">
  <section class="feedback-page-section">
    <h1 class="feedback-title">反馈与联系</h1>
    <p class="feedback-desc">
      我们欢迎您的反馈、建议或问题！请通过以下方式联系我们，或加入我们的用户群进行讨论：
    </p>
    <div class="feedback-contact-list">
      <div class="feedback-contact-item">
        <span class="feedback-label">邮箱：</span>
        <a href="mailto:gmshrekhelp@outlook.com" class="feedback-link">gmshrekhelp@outlook.com</a>
      </div>
      <div class="feedback-contact-item">
        <span class="feedback-label">QQ 群：</span>
        <span class="feedback-link">1005148851</span>
      </div>
      <div class="feedback-contact-item">
        <span class="feedback-label">GitHub Issues：</span>
        <a href="https://github.com/gmshrek/info/issues" class="feedback-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">gmshrek/info/issues</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feedback-tip">
      我们会尽快回复您的邮件。欢迎加入 QQ 群进行即时交流！
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .feedback-page-section {
      max-width: 480px;
      margin: 3rem auto 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px 0 rgba(60,60,120,0.08);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem 2rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .feedback-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
      color: #222;
    }
    .feedback-desc {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
    }
    .feedback-contact-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .feedback-contact-item {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #333;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .feedback-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #409EFF;
    }
    .feedback-link {
      font-family: monospace;
      color: #222;
      background: #f5f7fa;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 0.15em 0.6em;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.18s;
    }
    .feedback-link:hover {
      background: #e6f0fa;
      color: #409EFF;
    }
    .feedback-tip {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>
